Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/moshpitsurfer/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Add new snippets at snippets folder. Snippets at bundle/snipmate/snippets will
be ignored if a file with the same name exists in snippets

Add file-type specific plugins at ftplugins
